<item>
            <title>[HTTPCORE-612] NumberFormatException in DefaultConnectionReuseStrategy</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HTTPCORE-612</link>
                <project id="12310340" key="HTTPCORE">HttpComponents HttpCore</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;DefaultConnectionReuseStrategy uses Integer.parseInt to parse Content-Length header. For size &amp;gt; 2 GB, parsing fails with NumberFormatException. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Stack trace&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
parseInt:658, &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Integer&lt;/span&gt; (java.lang)
parseInt:776, &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Integer&lt;/span&gt; (java.lang)
keepAlive:136, DefaultConnectionReuseStrategy (org.apache.http.impl)
keepAlive:62, DefaultClientConnectionReuseStrategy (org.apache.http.impl.client)
execute:275, MainClientExec (org.apache.http.impl.execchain)
execute:186, ProtocolExec (org.apache.http.impl.execchain)
execute:89, RetryExec (org.apache.http.impl.execchain)
doExecute:185, InternalHttpClient (org.apache.http.impl.client)
execute:83, CloseableHttpClient (org.apache.http.impl.client) &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Line 90 &amp;amp; 136:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;final int contentLen = Integer.parseInt(clh.getValue());&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Should use Long.parseLong instead.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
